 occupation of the saints? Verse </div><div class="t m96f x27 he y6bd ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5, last part. </div><div class="t m1f3 x48 he y1f31 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9. </div><div class="t m1f01 x4e he y1b49 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What assurance is given in reference to these </div><div class="t m1e1b x27 he y190b ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">things? Verse 6, first part. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
